### Interactions API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Get All Reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Create New Review
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "gym": 1,
    "rating": 5,
    "comment": "Great gym with excellent facilities!"
}

### 3. Get Review Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Update Review (Owner only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/reviews/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "gym": 1,
    "rating": 4,
    "comment": "Updated review comment"
}

### 5. Delete Review
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reviews/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Report Review (Owner only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews/1/report/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Reply to Review (Owner only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "gym": 1,
    "rating": 5,
    "comment": "Thank you for your feedback!",
    "reply_to": 1
}

### 8. Get User Favorites
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Add Gym to Favorites
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "gym": 1
}

### 10. Get Favorite Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Remove from Favorites
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/favorites/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Get Gym Reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/?gym=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Get User Reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/?user=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
